      "description": "Presenting an impeccable E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a proactive VANOS overhaul, ensuring mechanical longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, paired with the factory variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its original damping characteristics and bushing integrity, delivering the precise, tactile steering feedback synonymous with this longitudinal rear-wheel-drive icon. A museum-quality example with a documented service history and no deferred maintenance.",
